title: The Dave Brubeck Quartet - The "Time Series" Albums
description:
These are the celebrated "Time Series" albums by The Dave Brubeck Quartet, which are:

Time Out (1959)
Time Further Out (1961)
Countdown: Time in Outer Space (1962)
Time Changes (1964)
Time In (1966)

Performer: The Dave Brubeck Quartet
Encoded: MP3 format, 256kbps CBR
Covers and scans of the booklets included
